<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="23Dec1923"><font color="red">23 December 1923</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): You will notice in the next extract and later than I shall write in a veiled way here and there explaining what critics did not observe in my last book and replying indirectly to their observations. </div>
